HEADWORD: Straightly
<hw>Straight"ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a right line; not
crookedly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Straightly</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Straightly
<hw>Straight"ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>A variant of
